00:41:08,750 --> 00:41:10,550
There was a free coupon?

512
00:41:10,550 --> 00:41:16,040
It's very important, more than anything, to comfort the other person.

513
00:41:16,040 --> 00:41:19,450
- Okay!
- And there must be some time given for the person to be alone.

514
00:41:19,450 --> 00:41:20,790
Why would you need some time alone?

515
00:41:20,790 --> 00:41:23,520
Some time to think and listen to some music alone.

516
00:41:23,520 --> 00:41:27,180
There must be these times for him/her to be able to love the other person more.

517
00:41:27,180 --> 00:41:32,950
No. I can't do that. Maybe after ten years, that would be possible.

518
00:41:32,950 --> 00:41:36,850
As for now, let me do that thing I want to do most.

519
00:41:55,550 --> 00:41:59,690
Will you, Oh Ha Na, take Choi Won to be your husband

520
00:41:59,690 --> 00:42:03,050
and live while loving and

521
00:42:03,050 --> 00:42:04,850
cherishing him for as long as you live?

522
00:42:04,850 --> 00:42:06,630
Yes.

523
00:42:09,970 --> 00:42:11,850
Will you, Choi Won,

524
00:42:11,850 --> 00:42:15,470
take Oh Ha Na as your wife, till death

525
00:42:15,470 --> 00:42:19,490
and love her even after that?

526
00:42:19,490 --> 00:42:21,800
Yes.

527
00:42:21,800 --> 00:42:24,060
But the pledge is intensifying... Fine!

528
00:42:24,060 --> 00:42:26,610
Will you, Oh Ha Na,

529
00:42:26,610 --> 00:42:30,170
even after death and being reborn,

530
00:42:30,170 --> 00:42:32,870
only love Choi Won?

531
00:42:32,870 --> 00:42:34,730
I promise.

532
00:42:34,730 --> 00:42:36,790
Me too.

533
00:43:04,950 --> 00:43:09,930
In this very familiar place, we must give our utmost effort.

534
00:43:09,930 --> 00:43:14,690
In order to fill the new moments with happiness.

535
00:43:18,350 --> 00:43:23,570
