537
00:43:28,330 --> 00:43:32,410
♬ Your eyes, nose, lips ♬
8 months later, summer

538
00:43:32,410 --> 00:43:33,800
Be quiet!

539
00:43:33,800 --> 00:43:37,150
♬ To the ends of your fingertips ♬

540
00:43:37,150 --> 00:43:39,250
