541
00:43:41,810 --> 00:43:46,280
♬ Your eyes, nose, lips
Your touch that used to touch me ♬

542
00:43:46,280 --> 00:43:50,340
♬ To the ends of your fingertips ♬

543
00:43:50,340 --> 00:43:55,000
Stop singing! Hey, why are you singing every morning?

544
00:43:55,000 --> 00:43:58,900
Oh, sorry. My excitement just came up without me knowing.

545
00:44:02,060 --> 00:44:06,850
♬Your eyes, nose, lips
our touch that used to touch me, to the ends of your fingertips ♬

546
00:44:06,850 --> 00:44:09,370
I...

547
00:44:09,370 --> 00:44:11,900
want to sleep quietly.

548
00:44:11,900 --> 00:44:16,320
Please sing in your mind. In your mind!

549
00:44:17,660 --> 00:44:21,720
Singing is best when you do it  aloud. What's wrong with you?

550
00:44:21,720 --> 00:44:24,790
In the morning from when I wake up to when I leave for work,

551
00:44:24,790 --> 00:44:29,510
I want to have a quiet morning time while thinking about what I have to do today. I told you that!

552
00:44:29,510 --> 00:44:32,410
But this time spent because you are singing...

553
00:44:32,410 --> 00:44:35,120
Return my morning time to me.

554
00:44:35,120 --> 00:44:37,150
- Return it!
- Hey.

555
00:44:37,150 --> 00:44:40,540
Living together is understanding and matching up to each other.

556
00:44:40,540 --> 00:44:46,270
Do you know how many times I woke up with my legs killing me because of you?

557
00:44:46,270 --> 00:44:47,320
I do what?

558
00:44:47,320 --> 00:44:49,460
From  when I'm falling asleep to when I wake up,

559
00:44:49,460 --> 00:44:52,560
my legs get numb because of how much you put yours over mine.

560
00:44:52,560 --> 00:44:56,160
How can you have just one permanent position from when you sleep to when you wake up?

561
00:44:56,160 --> 00:44:59,380
I didn't say anything because I liked having you beside me.

562
00:44:59,380 --> 00:45:03,310
You. You're trying to start something here, right?

563
00:45:11,080 --> 00:45:13,060
For today, only up to here.

564
00:45:24,780 --> 00:45:28,610
♬ Your eyes, nose, lips ♬

565
00:45:31,420 --> 00:45:33,830
Hey, Choi Won!

566
00:45:47,920 --> 00:45:50,250
Go away, or go to sleep.

567
00:45:50,250 --> 00:45:53,360
You're telling me to go away and go to sleep and leave this great sight?

568
00:45:53,360 --> 00:45:54,300
I can see a freckle!

569
00:45:54,300 --> 00:45:55,260
Where? Where, where?

570
00:45:55,260 --> 00:45:57,020
Cover it! Hurry!

571
00:45:57,020 --> 00:45:58,840
Aren't you going to go away?

572
00:46:00,490 --> 00:46:02,630
You're still pretty, even with the freckles.

573
00:46:06,050 --> 00:46:08,280
Wait! This matches better.

574
00:46:08,280 --> 00:46:11,270
Hey! Are you going to keep being like this?

575
00:46:20,600 --> 00:46:23,250
I'll check if the rice is ready.

576
00:46:30,010 --> 00:46:31,550
Go after you eat breakfast!

577
00:46:31,550 --> 00:46:33,550
I'm late and have no time because of whom?

578
00:46:33,550 --> 00:46:36,320
You can't. Your mom told me to make sure that you eat breakfast.

579
00:46:36,320 --> 00:46:38,830
I didn't eat breakfast well when I was at home either.

580
00:46:38,830 --> 00:46:40,440
Wait for a second.

581
00:46:46,690 --> 00:46:48,250
Here!

582
00:46:51,180 --> 00:46:54,880
This one or this one?

583
00:46:54,880 --> 00:46:56,840
- That one.
- This one?

584
00:47:03,160 --> 00:47:04,840
Left foot.

585
00:47:05,430 --> 00:47:07,310
You're all set.

586
00:47:08,390 --> 00:47:09,930
I'll be back.

587
00:47:09,930 --> 00:47:12,040
