588
00:47:15,010 --> 00:47:17,300
Come back safely!

589
00:47:17,300 --> 00:47:20,950
The "nation's shoes" project is a success.

590
00:47:20,950 --> 00:47:24,140
As expected, no matter how good an idea is, it's all about marketing, isn't it?

591
00:47:24,140 --> 00:47:28,160
I thought you'd slack off because it's a junior's idea. You worked hard.

592
00:47:28,160 --> 00:47:29,570
Yes, thank you.

593
00:47:29,570 --> 00:47:35,040
Prepare well for the second season. If it turns out well, I'll recommend you for a promotion. Do your best.

594
00:47:35,040 --> 00:47:38,520
Okay, I'll work hard, Director!

595
00:47:44,440 --> 00:47:47,010
I need to screenshoot this.

596
00:47:47,010 --> 00:47:50,200
Why would you screenshoot something like that?

597
00:47:50,200 --> 00:47:54,280
Why not? Even your face came out.

598
00:47:56,820 --> 00:47:59,990
Dae Bok, create our story too.

599
00:47:59,990 --> 00:48:01,020
I will.

600
00:48:01,020 --> 00:48:03,250
How are you going to draw me?

601
00:48:04,030 --> 00:48:10,090
Stay still. Since your cheeks are plump,

602
00:48:10,090 --> 00:48:14,520
