603
00:48:14,520 --> 00:48:18,810
Aigoo, it's already a masterpiece.

604
00:48:40,970 --> 00:48:43,600
No, this can't be happening!

605
00:48:43,600 --> 00:48:46,110
Choi Won! Won!

606
00:48:46,110 --> 00:48:47,900
What's wrong?

607
00:48:48,900 --> 00:48:50,030
What happened?

608
00:48:50,030 --> 00:48:52,110
Don't get any closer and listen from there.

609
00:48:52,110 --> 00:48:54,080
What now?

610
00:48:54,080 --> 00:48:59,180
I was out of my mind since I've been working on a new project, with an opportunity for a promotion.

611
00:48:59,180 --> 00:49:00,110
So what?

612
00:49:00,110 --> 00:49:04,850
I think something not on schedule has occurred. What do I do?

613
00:49:05,980 --> 00:49:08,550
I might need to go to the hospital.

614
00:49:08,550 --> 00:49:10,930
Are you maybe preg—

615
00:49:10,930 --> 00:49:14,970
Don't say anything to anyone! If it's true,

616
00:49:14,970 --> 00:49:17,380
what do I do?

617
00:49:17,380 --> 00:49:21,850
What do you mean? Let's worry about it together.

618
00:49:25,170 --> 00:49:27,770
You have my child!

619
00:49:27,770 --> 00:49:30,400
No way!

620
00:49:35,230 --> 00:49:39,250
Let's go to the hospital tomorrow after my flight, and tell your parents.

621
00:49:39,250 --> 00:49:40,490
I don't know.

622
00:49:40,490 --> 00:49:44,490
What do you mean you don't know? But is it a boy or a girl?

623
00:49:44,490 --> 00:49:47,260
Stupid. How would I know?

624
00:49:55,620 --> 00:49:57,640
It's so ugly.

625
00:49:57,640 --> 00:50:01,620
What are you talking about? I haven't seen a baby as pretty as her.

626
00:50:03,330 --> 00:50:06,800
Her nose is similar to mine.

627
00:50:07,700 --> 00:50:09,490
Hold her.

628
00:50:25,720 --> 00:50:32,630
Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Timeless Lovers @ Viki

629
00:50:55,000 --> 00:50:57,840
