634
00:51:16,590 --> 00:51:21,570
About our child...

635
00:51:26,960 --> 00:51:33,020
When I'm holding one of your hands, the baby's going to hold the other hand.

636
00:51:33,020 --> 00:51:36,850
At the same time, a baby on your back.

637
00:51:36,850 --> 00:51:38,980
A baby seated in front of you.

638
00:51:38,980 --> 00:51:42,870
I want to make a family just like that.

639
00:51:43,920 --> 00:51:45,750
Is that okay?

640
00:51:45,750 --> 00:51:48,050
So how many children is that?

641
00:51:48,050 --> 00:51:52,120
You said so last time, to prove it in the future.

642
00:51:52,940 --> 00:51:58,260
I will show my love to you by giving birth to children who look like us.

643
00:51:59,950 --> 00:52:03,920
Oh Ha Na, you really...

644
00:52:04,870 --> 00:52:08,500
In the future it's going to get really loud and chaotic.

645
00:52:08,500 --> 00:52:11,970
I will be yelling, and even from time to time...

646
00:52:11,970 --> 00:52:15,060
I probably won't be able to hold it in and will get really mad.

647
00:52:20,640 --> 00:52:22,140
That's okay.

648
00:52:22,140 --> 00:52:27,300
I'll help you with all of that.

649
00:52:27,300 --> 00:52:29,910
I'm still afraid.

650
00:52:30,940 --> 00:52:33,630
And everything's vague.

651
00:52:33,630 --> 00:52:36,150
That's okay, don't worry.

652
00:52:37,350 --> 00:52:39,290
Thanks, Ha Na.

653
00:52:40,320 --> 00:52:42,120
Thanks so much.

654
00:52:57,520 --> 00:53:00,640
You're picking a wedding ring, right?

655
00:53:00,640 --> 00:53:03,660
No, it isn't ours.

656
00:53:05,180 --> 00:53:07,460
I think that one and that one are good.

657
00:53:07,460 --> 00:53:09,560
Yeah, me too.

658
00:53:10,830 --> 00:53:12,630
Can you show us those?

659
00:53:18,210 --> 00:53:20,150
What is this?

660
00:53:23,710 --> 00:53:25,140
Are you giving these to us?

661
00:53:25,140 --> 00:53:26,660
Yes.

662
00:53:27,530 --> 00:53:29,860
And...

663
00:53:31,960 --> 00:53:34,090
Ha Na...

664
00:53:36,350 --> 00:53:39,670
